            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> Caesar Vespasianus Augustus pontifex ma<lb break="no" n="2"/>ximus <expan><abbr>tribunic</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>potest</abbr><ex>ate</ex></expan> VI <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> XIIII <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ater</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> censor <lb n="3"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> VI designatus VII <lb n="4"/>peditibus et equitibus qui militant in cohorti<lb break="no" n="5"/>bus decem quae appellantur I Antiochensi<lb break="no" n="6"/>um et I Sugambrorum veterana et I Raetorum <lb n="7"/>et I Lusitanorum et III et IV et V et VII et VIII Gallo<lb break="no" n="8"/>rum et Cisipadensium et sunt in Moesia sub <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>Sex</abbr><ex>to</ex></expan> Vettuleno Ceriale qui quina et vicena sti<lb break="no" n="10"/>pendia aut plura meruerant quorum nomina <lb n="11"/>subscripta sunt ipsis liberis posterisque eorum <lb n="12"/>civitatem dedit et conubium cum uxoribus quas <lb n="13"/>tunc habuissent cum est civitas iis data aut <lb n="14"/>si qui caelibes essent cum iis quas postea <lb n="15"/>duxissent dumtaxat singuli singulas <lb n="16"/><expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>nte</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>iem</ex></expan> IIII <expan><abbr>K</abbr><ex>alendas</ex></expan> Maias Caesare <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Domiti<lb break="no" n="17"/>ano III <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Pasidieno Firmo co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="18"/><expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> I Raetorum <lb n="19"/>cui prae<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>st</abbr></expan> <lb n="20"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Quintius Laberius Tutor Sabinianus <lb n="21"/>pediti <lb n="22"/>Herae Serapionis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Antioc</abbr><ex>hia</ex></expan> <lb n="23"/>descriptum et recognitum ex tabula aenea <expan><abbr>qua</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <lb n="24"/>fixa est Romae in Capitolio <expan><abbr>pos</abbr><ex>t</ex></expan> piscinam <lb n="25"/>in <expan><abbr>tribunal</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> deorum </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> Caesar Vespasianus Augustus pontifex maxi<lb break="no" n="2"/>mus <expan><abbr>tribunic</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>potest</abbr><ex>ate</ex></expan> VI <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> XIIII <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ater</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> censor <lb n="3"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> VI designatus VII <lb n="4"/>peditibus et equitibus qui militant in cohorti<lb break="no" n="5"/>bus decem quae appellantur I Antiochensi<lb break="no" n="6"/>um et I Sugambrorum veterana et I Raeto<lb break="no" n="7"/>rum et I Lusitanorum et III et IV et V et VII et VIII <lb n="8"/>Gallorum et Cisipadensium et sunt in Moesia <lb n="9"/>sub <expan><abbr>Sex</abbr><ex>to</ex></expan> Vettuleno Ceriale qui quina et vicena <lb n="10"/>stipendia aut plura meruerant quorum nomi<lb break="no" n="11"/>na subscripta sunt ipsis liberis posterisque eo<lb break="no" n="12"/>rum civitatem dedit et conubium cum uxori<lb break="no" n="13"/>bus quas tunc habuissent cum est civitas iis <lb n="14"/>data aut si qui cael<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>bes</abbr></expan> essent cum iis quas <lb n="15"/>postea duxissent dumtaxat singuli </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> singulas <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>nte</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>iem</ex></expan> IIII <expan><abbr>K</abbr><ex>alendas</ex></expan> Maias Caesare <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Domitiano III <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Pasidieno Firmo co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> I Raetoriae <note>sic</note> <lb n="4"/>cui prae<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>st</abbr></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Quintius Laberius Tutor Sabinianus <lb n="6"/>pediti <lb n="7"/>Herae Serapionis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Antioc</abbr><ex>hia</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>descriptum et recognitum ex tabula aenea quae <lb n="9"/>fixa est Romae in Capitolio </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> Domiti <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ili</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Col</abbr><ex>lina</ex></expan> Veri <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> Coeli <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ili</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fal</abbr><ex>erna</ex></expan> Bruti Rufi <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> Iuli Lentuli <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> Aquili <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ili</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Vol</abbr><ex>tinia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Campan</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> Lossi <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ili</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Gal</abbr><ex>eria</ex></expan> Severi <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Sex</abbr><ex>ti</ex></expan> Lossi <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ili</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Gal</abbr><ex>eria</ex></expan> Apollinaris <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> Atini <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ili</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Vel</abbr><ex>ina</ex></expan> Augustalis
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>ILJug: keine Zeilenfälle angegeben; wiederholte Textteile innerhalb des Diploms nur einmal wiedergegeben. (B): tab. I extrinsecus: ILJug: Z. 2/3: p(ater) p(atriae) co(n)s(ul); Vučković-Todorović: Z. 17: Passidieno; AE 1968: Z. 17: co(n)ss(ulibus); AE 1980: Z. 19: prae(e)s; tab. I intus: LJug: Z. 2/3: p(ater) p(atriae) co(n)s(ul); Vučković-Todorović: Z. 7: IV et V VII; tab. II intus: Vučković-Todorović: Z. 2: Passidieno.</p>
